Asia
---
Philippines (South Cotabato Province). 31 Jan 2020. (Suspected) at least 40 cases in the Puroks 3, 4 and 7 of Maltana localities.
https://www.mindanews.com/top-stories/2020/01/chikungunya-on-the-rise-in-south-cotabato/

